text.tspan: Experimental mapping using a weaving approach
visualizing modes of daily travel in the City of Toronto -
showing bicycle, car, transit, and walk all on one map!
Tomorrow Survey. This map includes all trips (except
recreational walk trips) made by residents aged 5
years and older. Data were aggregated to tiles based
on the home-location of survey respondents.
Map by Jeff Allen in 06/2025 using QGIS, Inkscape,
